name: Bears Ears Child & Family Therapy
adCopy: Serving all of Tooele county's families since 1907, Bear's Ears Child & Family Therapy is sure to help with all your therapy needs. Our trained doctors love to help, heal, and and here for you always.

name: Gentry Finance
adCopy: Need a second look at your budget? Or maybe looking for a corporate loan? Gentry Finance is the business for offering. Offering low interest rates, friendly representatives, and years of practice we're sure you'll love your experience with us.

adCopy: The luxury stay and suite in all of Tooele County. Friends or family coming to visit? Wedding night? Home repossessed? Whatever the occassion, the Kirk Hotel has your housing needs covered! Stay the night in one of our hotel rooms, or make it a longer experience in our apartments.
